SE98 Plymouth theme Installation

To prepare the theme for your resolution run "make" awk script by running "./make" or "awk -f make".
It will create "se98" subfolder, get resolution of your X or Wayland GUI screen, render the background image and throbber from svg-files.
When done, run these commands:
sudo cp -r "$PWD/se98" /usr/share/plymouth/themes
sudo plymouth-set-default-theme -R se98
To preview run:
sudo ./test-plymouth